8 months, you can extend the measurement range to 6×6 inches. In all these cases, the decal size for shirts should be only one inch below the neckline.</span></p><p class="sc-xiLah fvOkQT pf-64_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-66_"><span style="font-weight: 700;">2. Toddler
